replies.body:
Sorry I kind of abuse freelo

1. {{champion:42}} 
What kind of ADC deals 3 types of damage without red buff? ROFL CORKI. Magic damage, physical damage, true damage. WTF. Yea no one plays him because I don't know why. He has high range poke (R) and can use Q or R to check brushes. AND WHAT THE FK he has a (not) reliable escape as well. This champion scales so well with double buffs it's amazeballs. Even though he hasn't got me to Silver IV yet I still think he's an OP champ. I once had a 5/1 W/L with him in solo queue. 

2. {{champion:412}} 
I just learnt him since he's free this week, but I see this really high potential of carrying idiot ADCs with this champion. Seriously, If you can predict the enemy's movement, your hooks are so easy to land. SOMEONE GIFT ME THIS CHAMPION LOL
I like to get ignite on this champion because you already deal so much damage with your hooks and flay and box. If the enemy ADC is half HP while I'm like 3/4 HP, I'd gladly trap him in my box and flay them out of my box for the slow and hook them and ignite them. I proceed to type "/all 1v1 me, idiots" in chat. No I am not toxic.

3. {{champion:40}} 
Mainly because it's hilarious to see enemy team raging because they can't reach my ADC (AKA NEWBORN BABY) to kill them. AD Steroid shield and the ult that heals. Sorry boys, better ban Janna. Too bad no one bans Janna in my ELO. 

